'''30秒上火星'''（英文：Thirty Seconds to Mars 或 30 Seconds to Mars）是一支来自[[美國|美国]][[加州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉矶]]，于1998年创立的[[搖滾|摇滚]]乐队。<span data-segmentid="82" class="cx-segment">乐队现成员包括兄弟[[杰瑞德·莱托|杰瑞德·莱托]](主唱、吉他、贝斯、键盘)与[[香农·莱托|香农·雷托]](鼓、打击乐器)。 </span><span data-segmentid="85" class="cx-segment">在其历史发展过程中，该乐队经历了一系列</span><span data-segmentid="82" class="cx-segment">的</span><span data-segmentid="85" class="cx-segment">成员变更。</span>

<span data-segmentid="86" class="cx-segment">该乐队的首张专辑''[[30秒上火星_(专辑)|《30秒上火星》]]'' (2002年)，由制作人[[Bob_Ezrin|Bob Ezrin]]参与制作并在发行后获得了相当正面的评价，但它在商业上的成就却很有限。 </span><span data-segmentid="89" class="cx-segment">通过释出第二张专辑''[[A_Beautiful_Lie|《美丽的谎言》]]'' (2005年)，该乐队在世界范围拥有了名声。这张专辑在世界上的多个地区获得了[[音乐唱片销售认证列表|销量认证]]。他们的下一张专辑</span><span data-segmentid="92" class="cx-segment">''[[This_Is_War|《全面开战》]]'' (2009年)，标志着该乐队在音乐风格上的一个戏剧性的演变，因为它融入了[[實驗音樂|实验音乐]]的影响并更为兼容并蓄。因该乐队与其唱片公司</span><span data-segmentid="95" class="cx-segment">[[EMI|EMI]]陷入了一场重大的法律纠纷，该专辑的制作过程备受关注，而这一事件也最终成为纪录片''[[Artifact_(film)|《手工制品》]]'' (2012年)的主要内容。 随后，30</span><span data-segmentid="98" class="cx-segment">秒</span><span data-segmentid="95" class="cx-segment">上</span><span data-segmentid="98" class="cx-segment">火</span><span data-segmentid="95" class="cx-segment">星转至</span><span data-segmentid="98" class="cx-segment">[[环球音乐集团|环球音乐集团]]旗下，发行了第四张专辑''[[Love,_Lust,_Faith_and_Dreams|《爱 欲 信 + 梦》]]''  (2013年)并获得了在评论界与商业表现上的成功。 他们的第五张专辑</span><span data-segmentid="101" class="cx-segment">''[[America_(Thirty_Seconds_to_Mars_album)|《美利坚》]]'' (2018年)，则在发行后收到了两极分化的评价。</span>

<span data-segmentid="103" class="cx-segment">截至2014年9月，该乐队已经在全球范围内售出专辑超过一千五百万份。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.digitaljournal.com/a-and-e/music/review-jared-leto-performs-new-single-do-or-die-on-ellen/article/405764|title=Jared Leto performs new single 'Do or Die' on 'Ellen'|accessdate=September 28, 2014|author=Papadatos|date=September 27, 2014|first=Markos|publisher=Digital Journal|archive-date=2020-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004195730/http://www.digitaljournal.com/a-and-e/music/review-jared-leto-performs-new-single-do-or-die-on-ellen/article/405764/|dead-url=no}}</ref> </span><span data-segmentid="104" class="cx-segment">一直以来</span><span data-segmentid="103" class="cx-segment">，</span><span data-segmentid="104" class="cx-segment">30秒上火星</span><span data-segmentid="103" class="cx-segment">的</span><span data-segmentid="104" class="cx-segment">巡回演出</span><span data-segmentid="103" class="cx-segment">常常售罄，</span><span data-segmentid="104" class="cx-segment">他们也担任过无数音乐节与摇滚节的压轴演出嘉宾。</span> <span data-segmentid="105" class="cx-segment">该</span><span data-segmentid="104" class="cx-segment">乐队因其</span><span data-segmentid="105" class="cx-segment">充满活力的现场表演</span><span data-segmentid="104" class="cx-segment">以及对多种音乐</span><span data-segmentid="105" class="cx-segment">流派</span><span data-segmentid="104" class="cx-segment">元素的运用</span><span data-segmentid="105" class="cx-segment">，</span><span data-segmentid="104" class="cx-segment">并以</span><span data-segmentid="105" class="cx-segment">其带来哲思和精神力量的歌词，[[概念專輯|概念专辑]]以及实验性的音乐而备受赞誉。<ref name="allmusic">{{Cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/thirty-seconds-to-mars-mn0000485365/biography|title=Thirty Seconds to Mars|accessdate=May 18, 2013|author=Leahey|first=Andrew|publisher=[[AllMusic|AllMusic]]. [[All_Media_Network|All Media Network]]|archive-date=2018-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003112427/https://www.allmusic.com/artist/thirty-seconds-to-mars-mn0000485365/biography|dead-url=no}}</ref> 30</span><span data-segmentid="107" class="cx-segment">秒</span><span data-segmentid="105" class="cx-segment">上</span><span data-segmentid="107" class="cx-segment">火星</span><span data-segmentid="105" class="cx-segment">在其生涯历史上</span><span data-segmentid="107" class="cx-segment">收到了</span><span data-segmentid="105" class="cx-segment">不少</span><span data-segmentid="107" class="cx-segment">奖项</span><span data-segmentid="105" class="cx-segment">与</span><span data-segmentid="107" class="cx-segment">荣誉，</span><span data-segmentid="105" class="cx-segment">其中</span><span data-segmentid="107" class="cx-segment">包括一个[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]。他们也登上了杂志''[[Kerrang!|Kerrang!]]'' 评出的2000-2010年最佳艺人榜单。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Carter|first=Emily|title=The 60 Biggest Bands On The Planet Right Now|url=http://www.kerrang.com/21888/60-biggest-bands-planet-right-now/|accessdate=May 12, 2015|work=[[Kerrang!|Kerrang!]]|date=December 15, 2014|archive-date=2017-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170719111606/http://www.kerrang.com/21888/60-biggest-bands-planet-right-now/|dead-url=no}}</ref></span>

== 历史 ==

=== 1998-2000年：乐队成立与早期生涯 ===
<span data-segmentid="112" class="cx-segment">30秒上火星于1998年在美国加利福尼亚州洛杉矶成立，最早是作为兄弟 [[杰瑞德·雷托|杰瑞德·雷托]]和[[香农·萊托|香农·雷托]]两人之间的合作——两人从童年时期开始就已经在一起演奏和创作音乐。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.houstonianonline.com/a-e/30-seconds-to-mars-leads-forever-night-never-day-tour-1.387040|title=30 Seconds to Mars Leads "Forever Night, Never Day" Tour|accessdate=May 12, 2015|author=Edwards|date=March 21, 2006|first=Kristin|work=Houstonian|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120312092308/http://www.houstonianonline.com/a-e/30-seconds-to-mars-leads-forever-night-never-day-tour-1.387040|archivedate=2012-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref> 随着</span><span data-segmentid="116" class="cx-segment">吉他手[[Solon_Bixler|索伦·比克斯勒]]和贝斯手[[Matt_Wachter|马特·沃赫特]]的加入，这一双人组合后来扩充为四人乐队。辅助</span><span data-segmentid="119" class="cx-segment">吉他手[[Kevin_Drake|凯文·德雷克]]，原本为了成为乐队的贝斯手而试演，后来也加入成为了乐队的巡演乐手。</span><span data-segmentid="121" class="cx-segment">在</span><span data-segmentid="119" class="cx-segment">最早</span><span data-segmentid="121" class="cx-segment">的演出里，该乐队采用了好几个不同的名称，最终才确名为“30秒上火星”。据称，这一名称来源于一本题为''Argus Apocraphex''的罕见[[手抄本|手抄本]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.confrontmagazine.com/main/09-2006/library/transcript3.html|title=Matt Wachter, Tomo Milicevic – 30 Seconds to Mars|accessdate=August 29, 2013|date=June 28, 2006|work=Confront Magazine|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070910022910/http://www.confrontmagazine.com/main/09-2006/library/transcript3.html|archivedate=2007-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref></span> <span data-segmentid="123" class="cx-segment">杰瑞德·雷托将乐队名</span><span data-segmentid="121" class="cx-segment">称</span><span data-segmentid="123" class="cx-segment">描述为“来自书中的一个指代，一个粗略</span><span data-segmentid="121" class="cx-segment">的转译</span><span data-segmentid="123" class="cx-segment">。</span><span data-segmentid="124" class="cx-segment">我觉得这个想法很有趣，它是一个</span><span data-segmentid="123" class="cx-segment">对</span><span data-segmentid="124" class="cx-segment">未来</span><span data-segmentid="123" class="cx-segment">的比喻</span><span data-segmentid="124" class="cx-segment">，</span><span data-segmentid="123" class="cx-segment">”</span><span data-segmentid="124" class="cx-segment">他解释说。</span> <span data-segmentid="123" class="cx-segment">“</span><span data-segmentid="124" class="cx-segment">30秒上火星——指‘</span><span data-segmentid="125" class="cx-segment">我们</span><span data-segmentid="124" class="cx-segment">离</span><span data-segmentid="125" class="cx-segment">一些不可触及的东西是如此地接近</span><span data-segmentid="124" class="cx-segment">’</span><span data-segmentid="125" class="cx-segment">的事实。</span><span data-segmentid="124" class="cx-segment">与此同时</span><span data-segmentid="125" class="cx-segment">，</span><span data-segmentid="124" class="cx-segment">‘</span><span data-segmentid="126" class="cx-segment">火星</span><span data-segmentid="125" class="cx-segment">’作为‘</span><span data-segmentid="126" class="cx-segment">战神</span><span data-segmentid="125" class="cx-segment">’的说法也</span><span data-segmentid="126" class="cx-segment">很有</span><span data-segmentid="125" class="cx-segment">趣</span><span data-segmentid="126" class="cx-segment">。 在这里</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">你可以用这些</span><span data-segmentid="126" class="cx-segment">说法</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">来替代和解释，但是</span><span data-segmentid="126" class="cx-segment">对于</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">我</span><span data-segmentid="126" class="cx-segment">和我哥哥来说，重要的是</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">，它是</span><span data-segmentid="126" class="cx-segment">一个富有</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">想象力</span><span data-segmentid="126" class="cx-segment">的短语，能够以</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">一</span><span data-segmentid="126" class="cx-segment">种尽可能</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">独特的方式</span><span data-segmentid="126" class="cx-segment">来代表我们的音乐</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">。</span><span data-segmentid="126" class="cx-segment">”</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment"><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ink19.com/issues/november2005/interviews/30SecondsToMars.html|title=30 Seconds To Mars|accessdate=August 29, 2013|author=Cray|date=November 2005|first=Jen|publisher=Ink 19|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924035107/http://www.ink19.com/issues/november2005/interviews/30SecondsToMars.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref></span> <span data-segmentid="128" class="cx-segment">在他的描述中，这个名称“适用于几个不同的</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">层面</span><span data-segmentid="128" class="cx-segment">，是一个</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">诗意的</span><span data-segmentid="128" class="cx-segment">，充满暗示的，</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">具有</span><span data-segmentid="128" class="cx-segment">电影</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">感的</span><span data-segmentid="128" class="cx-segment">，并</span><span data-segmentid="127" class="cx-segment">能够带来直接感受的短语（a phrase that is lyrical, suggestive, cinematic, and filled with immediacy）。”</span><span data-segmentid="128" class="cx-segment"><ref name="shoutweb4">{{Cite web|url=http://www.shoutweb.com/interviews/30secondstomars0502.phtml|title=30 Seconds To Mars: Welcome To Their Universe|accessdate=August 29, 2013|author=Redmon|date=May 10, 2002|first=Jess|publisher=Shoutweb.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080430075630/http://www.shoutweb.com/interviews/30secondstomars0502.phtml|archivedate=2008-04-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref></span> <span data-segmentid="129" class="cx-segment">在30秒</span><span data-segmentid="128" class="cx-segment">上火星</span><span data-segmentid="129" class="cx-segment">的早期生涯</span><span data-segmentid="128" class="cx-segment">里</span><span data-segmentid="129" class="cx-segment">，杰瑞德·雷托不允许他作为好莱坞演员的事实被使用在乐队的宣传中。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=30 Seconds to Mars|last=Tagliaferro|first=Lauren|date=June 23, 2006|quote=Not content to be defined merely as "Jared Leto's band," 30 Seconds to Mars has fought to be respected as a group of formidable musicians – even refusing to play at venues that use Leto's movie-star status to promote them.}}</ref></span>

<span data-segmentid="130" class="cx-segment">1998年及以前，该乐队在美国的小型场馆和俱乐部中演出。</span><span data-segmentid="131" class="cx-segment">他们的同名首张专辑的制作已经进行了好几年，由杰瑞德·雷托谱写其中的大部分歌曲。 </span><span data-segmentid="132" class="cx-segment">在此期间乐队录制了</span><span data-segmentid="131" class="cx-segment">一些样本歌曲，比如''Valhalla''、''Revolution''、''Jupiter''</span><span data-segmentid="132" class="cx-segment">和</span><span data-segmentid="131" class="cx-segment">''Hero''</span><span data-segmentid="132" class="cx-segment">——后</span><span data-segmentid="131" class="cx-segment">两者</span><span data-segmentid="132" class="cx-segment">分别更名为''Fallen''和''Year Zero''并出现在乐队的首张专辑里</span><span data-segmentid="131" class="cx-segment">。</span><span data-segmentid="132" class="cx-segment">样本</span><span data-segmentid="131" class="cx-segment">歌曲''Buddha''</span> ''<span data-segmentid="132" class="cx-segment">for Mary</span>''<span data-segmentid="131" class="cx-segment">也得到重新制作，加入到正式的首张专辑中</span><span data-segmentid="132" class="cx-segment">。<ref name="shoutweb4"/></span><span data-segmentid="133" class="cx-segment">他们的</span><span data-segmentid="132" class="cx-segment">作品让</span><span data-segmentid="133" class="cx-segment">一些唱片公司</span><span data-segmentid="132" class="cx-segment">对于签约30</span><span data-segmentid="133" class="cx-segment">秒</span><span data-segmentid="132" class="cx-segment">上</span><span data-segmentid="133" class="cx-segment">火星</span><span data-segmentid="132" class="cx-segment">充满兴趣</span><span data-segmentid="133" class="cx-segment">，</span><span data-segmentid="132" class="cx-segment">最终他们与厂牌</span><span data-segmentid="133" class="cx-segment">[[Immortal_Records|Immortal Records]]签约。<ref name="chartattack">{{Cite web|url=http://www.chartattack.com/DAMN/2002/04/0103.cfm|title=Jared Leto: From Hollywood To Mars|accessdate=July 22, 2011|author=Bento|date=April 1, 2002|first=Debbie|work=[[ChartAttack|ChartAttack]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20020507052412/http://www.chartattack.com/DAMN/2002/04/0103.cfm|archivedate=2002-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref></span> <span data-segmentid="135" class="cx-segment">1999年，[[維京唱片|维京唱片]]加入了这份合同。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1044420/virgin-sues-30-seconds-to-mars-for-30-million|title=Virgin Sues 30 Seconds To Mars For $30 Million|accessdate=August 29, 2013|author=Paine|date=August 18, 2008|first=Andre|work=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124112728/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1044420/virgin-sues-30-seconds-to-mars-for-30-million|dead-url=no}}</ref></span>

