=== <span data-segmentid="137" class="cx-segment">2001-2003年：首张专辑</span> ===
{{Listen|filename=<!-- 檔案不存在 Thirty Seconds to Mars - Edge of the Earth.ogg ，可從英文維基百科取得 -->|title="Edge of the Earth"|description=''Edge of the Earth''来自乐队的同名首张专辑，混合了来自多种音乐流派和音乐风格的元素。}}<span data-segmentid="154" class="cx-segment">在2001年，30秒上火星投身到怀俄明州乡间录制他们的首张专辑，与制作人[[Bob_Ezrin|Bob Ezrin]]和[[Brian_Virtue|Brian Virtue]]合作。由于</span><span data-segmentid="157" class="cx-segment">他们从小听</span><span data-segmentid="154" class="cx-segment">Ezrin与</span><span data-segmentid="157" class="cx-segment">[[平克·弗洛伊德|平克·弗洛伊德]]、[[Kiss合唱團|Kiss合唱团]]及[[埃利斯·库珀|埃利斯·库珀]]合作的作品长大，同时他们觉得他是唯一一个能在首张专辑中帮助他们获得想要的空间感受和宏大效果的人，他们选择了与Bob Ezrin合作。<ref name="shoutweb4"/> 乐队</span><span data-segmentid="161" class="cx-segment">在一个面积约为15000英亩的空仓库里录音，希望选择这样的地点能够提升他们的音乐。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bandchat.org/articles/2004/30stm.html|title=30 Seconds to Mars Interview|accessdate=August 29, 2013|publisher=Bandchat.org|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221503/http://www.bandchat.org/articles/2004/30stm.html|archivedate=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 在这张专辑释出之前，乐队</span><span data-segmentid="162" class="cx-segment">[[Puddle_of_Mudd|Puddle of Mudd]]便已邀请30秒上火星为他们于2002年春天为期六周的巡演进行开场表演。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1453021/puddle-of-mudd-deliver-no-frills-rock-at-philly-date/|title=Puddle Of Mudd Deliver No-Frills Rock At Philly Date|accessdate=May 26, 2014|author=Jordan|date=March 22, 2002|first=Chris|publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]. [[Viacom_Media_Networks|Viacom Media Networks]]|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102200211/http://www.mtv.com/news/1453021/puddle-of-mudd-deliver-no-frills-rock-at-philly-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 随后，该乐队</span><span data-segmentid="164" class="cx-segment">开</span><span data-segmentid="162" class="cx-segment">启了为</span><span data-segmentid="164" class="cx-segment">乐队[[Incubus|Incubus]]开场的北美巡演，并在八月进行了一系列的俱乐部演出。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://gauntlet.ucalgary.ca/story/8596|title=30 Seconds to Mars|accessdate=May 26, 2014|author=Atkinson|date=October 3, 2002|first=Myke|work=[[Gauntlet_(newspaper)|Gauntlet]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080513025441/http://gauntlet.ucalgary.ca/story/8596|archivedate=2008-05-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref></span>

<span data-segmentid="166" class="cx-segment">通过厂牌[[Immortal_Records|Immortal]]和[[維京唱片|维京唱片]]，该乐队在2002年8月27日在美国发行了他们的第一张专辑''[[30秒上火星_(专辑)|《30秒上火星》]]''。</span><span data-segmentid="170" class="cx-segment">杰瑞德·雷托</span><span data-segmentid="166" class="cx-segment">将这张专辑描述</span><span data-segmentid="170" class="cx-segment">为一</span><span data-segmentid="166" class="cx-segment">张主题是“人的斗争和自我决断”的</span><span data-segmentid="170" class="cx-segment">[[概念專輯|概念专辑]] ，其中以超凡脱俗的元素和概念式的想法来表现人的真实境况。<ref name="shoutweb4"/> 这张</span><span data-segmentid="172" class="cx-segment">专辑在美国售出了121000张，</span><span data-segmentid="170" class="cx-segment">在美国</span><span data-segmentid="172" class="cx-segment">[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌两百强专辑榜]]中取得107名，并在美国[[Top_Heatseekers|公告牌Top Heatseekers榜]]取得了第一名。<ref name="2002charts">{{Cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/30-seconds-to-mars-mw0000223814/awards|title=30 Seconds to Mars: Awards|accessdate=April 23, 2013|publisher=AllMusic. All Media Network|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308025748/http://www.allmusic.com/album/30-seconds-to-mars-mw0000223814/awards|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Mission to Mars: Blasts Off Again|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_billboard_2006-08-26_118_34/page/n35|last=Lear|first=Courtney|date=August 26, 2006|journal=Billboard|issue=34|volume=118|page=34}}</ref></span> <span data-segmentid="175" class="cx-segment">在此之前</span><span data-segmentid="172" class="cx-segment">发行的单曲</span><span data-segmentid="175" class="cx-segment">[[Capricorn_(A_Brand_New_Name)|''Capricorn (A Brand New Name)'']]，在美国[[Mainstream_Rock_(chart)|公告牌主流摇滚歌曲榜]]中最高取得了第31名。<ref name="2002charts" /></span><span data-segmentid="178" class="cx-segment">''30秒上火星'' 的发行收到了大体积极的评价；<ref name="10years2">{{Cite journal|title=10 Years of Life on Mars|last=Winwood|first=Ian|date=February 18, 2012|journal=Kerrang!|issue=1402|page=22}}</ref> 音乐评论家Megan O'Toole认为乐队“成功地为自己在摇滚领域里开拓了独一无二的位置（managed to carve out a unique niche for themselves in the rock realm）”。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=30 Seconds to Mars|url=http://www.gazette.uwo.ca/2002/September/26/arts_and_entertainment2.htm|last=O'Toole|first=Megan|date=September 26, 2002|accessdate=May 29, 2014|issue=17|volume=96|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030419215415/http://www.gazette.uwo.ca/2002/September/26/arts_and_entertainment2.htm|archivedate=2003-04-19|journal=|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 这张</span><span data-segmentid="179" class="cx-segment">专辑慢热地取得了成功，截至2011年3月，它最终在全球销售了两百万份。<ref name="MarsAttacks">{{Cite journal|title=Mars Attacks|last=Evans|first=Mark|date=March 2011|journal=What's On|publisher=[[Motivate_Publishing|Motivate Publishing]]|issue=395|page=29}}</ref></span>

<span data-segmentid="180" class="cx-segment">2002年10月，该乐队与[[I_Mother_Earth|I Mother Earth]]和[[Billy_Talent|Billy Talent]]一同进行了MTV Campus Invation巡演。 11月，30秒上</span><span data-segmentid="183" class="cx-segment">火星在电视</span><span data-segmentid="180" class="cx-segment">节目</span><span data-segmentid="183" class="cx-segment">''[[Last_Call_with_Carson_Daly|Last Call with Carson Daly]]上演出，''</span><span data-segmentid="180" class="cx-segment">完成了他们的荧幕首秀</span><span data-segmentid="183" class="cx-segment">；他们为</span><span data-segmentid="180" class="cx-segment">乐队</span><span data-segmentid="183" class="cx-segment">[[Our_Lady_Peace|Our Lady Peace]]和[[Sevendust|Sevendust]]进行开场表演。歌曲</span><span data-segmentid="187" class="cx-segment">[[Edge_of_the_Earth|''Edge of the Earth'']]在2003年发布，成为这张专辑中的第二支单曲。</span><span data-segmentid="189" class="cx-segment">2003年年初，</span><span data-segmentid="187" class="cx-segment">比克斯勒</span><span data-segmentid="189" class="cx-segment">退出了乐队，原因</span><span data-segmentid="187" class="cx-segment">与之前巡演</span><span data-segmentid="189" class="cx-segment">里出现的一些</span><span data-segmentid="187" class="cx-segment">问题</span><span data-segmentid="189" class="cx-segment">相关。</span><span data-segmentid="187" class="cx-segment">后来，</span><span data-segmentid="190" class="cx-segment">他被成功通过试演的</span><span data-segmentid="189" class="cx-segment">吉他手</span><span data-segmentid="190" class="cx-segment">[[Tomo_Miličević|托莫·米利塞维奇]]所替代。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://kaos2000.net/interviews/30stm/tomomatt/|title=Interview with Tomo Milicevic and Matt Wachter of 30 Seconds to Mars|accessdate=August 29, 2013|author=Anderson|date=April 19, 2006|first=Philip|work=Kaos2000 Magazine|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65jnMrjoQ?url=http://kaos2000.net/interviews/30stm/tomomatt/|archive-date=2012-02-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref></span> <span data-segmentid="192" class="cx-segment">该乐队随后与乐队[[Chevelle_(band)|Chevelle]]、[[Trust_Company_(band)|Trust Company]]及[[Shihad|Pacifier]]进行巡演，并参与了2003年的[[Lollapalooza|Lollapalooza]]巡演。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://rockdirt.com/lollapalooza-tour-stops-in-irvine/7259/|title=Lollapalooza Tour Stops In Irvine|accessdate=August 6, 2010|date=August 19, 2003|publisher=Rockdirt.com|archive-date=2011-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522015612/http://rockdirt.com/lollapalooza-tour-stops-in-irvine/7259/|dead-url=no}}</ref></span>

=== 2004-2008年：《美丽的谎言》 ===
{{Listen|filename=<!-- 檔案不存在 Thirty Seconds to Mars - The Kill.ogg ，可從英文維基百科取得 -->|title="The Kill"|description=''The Kill''受到90年代另类摇滚的强烈影响。这是专辑“美丽的谎言”中的第二首单曲。}}<span data-segmentid="214" class="cx-segment">30秒上火星于2004年3月重返录音室，与音乐制作人[[Josh_Abraham|Josh Abraham]]一起进行第二张专辑''[[A_Beautiful_Lie|《美丽的谎言》]]''</span>的制作。<span data-segmentid="214" class="cx-segment"><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.melodic.net/?page=news&id=2260|title=30 Seconds To Mars Working On Next Album|accessdate=August 29, 2013|author=Roth|date=March 16, 2004|first=Kaj|work=[[Melodic_(magazine)|Melodic]]|archive-date=2013-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923034038/http://www.melodic.net/?page=news&id=2260|dead-url=no}}</ref></span> <span data-segmentid="217" class="cx-segment">在</span><span data-segmentid="214" class="cx-segment">录音制作的过程</span><span data-segmentid="217" class="cx-segment">中，</span><span data-segmentid="214" class="cx-segment">为了配合<span data-segmentid="217" class="cx-segment">杰瑞德·雷托的演艺事业，乐队跟随</span></span><span data-segmentid="217" class="cx-segment">前往了四个不同的大陆。''《''</span><span data-segmentid="218" class="cx-segment">''美丽的谎言》''在曲风和歌词上都与乐队的首张专辑有巨大的不同。 “</span><span data-segmentid="219" class="cx-segment">在第一张专辑里，我建立了一个世界，然后躲在里面，”雷托说。 </span><span data-segmentid="220" class="cx-segment">"</span><span data-segmentid="219" class="cx-segment">而对于</span><span data-segmentid="220" class="cx-segment">''《美丽的谎言》''，是时候转向一种更为私人化，没那么理性化的方式。</span> <span data-segmentid="221" class="cx-segment">尽管这张专辑中仍然充满了概念式的元素和主题化的想法，它最终还是更多地围绕内心，而不是头脑（much more wrapped around the heart than the head）。 </span><span data-segmentid="220" class="cx-segment">它</span><span data-segmentid="222" class="cx-segment">关于残酷的诚实、成长、改变。 </span><span data-segmentid="221" class="cx-segment">它及其亲近地探讨了</span><span data-segmentid="223" class="cx-segment">处在选择之中的</span><span data-segmentid="222" class="cx-segment">人的</span><span data-segmentid="223" class="cx-segment">命运</span><span data-segmentid="222" class="cx-segment">，是一次</span><span data-segmentid="224" class="cx-segment">原始</span><span data-segmentid="223" class="cx-segment">的情感</span><span data-segmentid="224" class="cx-segment">旅程。</span><span data-segmentid="225" class="cx-segment">一个</span><span data-segmentid="224" class="cx-segment">关于</span><span data-segmentid="225" class="cx-segment">生活</span><span data-segmentid="224" class="cx-segment">、</span><span data-segmentid="225" class="cx-segment">爱情、死亡、痛苦、快乐和激情</span><span data-segmentid="224" class="cx-segment">的故事</span><span data-segmentid="225" class="cx-segment">。</span><span data-segmentid="226" class="cx-segment">它</span><span data-segmentid="225" class="cx-segment">关于‘人之所以为人’的一切</span><span data-segmentid="226" class="cx-segment">。</span><span data-segmentid="225" class="cx-segment">”</span><span data-segmentid="226" class="cx-segment"><ref name="nbcu2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.usanetwork.com/series/virginrecords/theshow/characterprofiles/30seconds/bio.html|title=30 Seconds to Mars|accessdate=August 29, 2013|publisher=[[USA_Network|USA Network]]. [[NBCUniversal|NBCUniversal]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070530021651/http://www.usanetwork.com/series/virginrecords/theshow/characterprofiles/30seconds/bio.html|archivedate=2007-05-30|dead-url=no}}</ref></span>[[File:Jaredletoinconcert2006.jpg|thumb]][[夏洛特_(北卡羅來納州)|夏洛特]]演出]]
''《美丽的谎言》''于2005年8月30日在美国发行。因为这张专辑在发行前便遭受泄露，故乐队决定在专辑里增加两首额外的歌曲''Battle of One''及''Hunter''（对[[碧玉_(歌手)|碧玉]]歌曲的翻唱）。为了行销此张专辑，乐队还决定随机在专辑内附上12张“金门票”，抽到金門票即可在任何一場30秒上火星的演唱會中免費入場，並獲得進入演唱會後台的機會。<span data-segmentid="227" class="cx-segment">之后，这张专辑共售出超过四百万份，</span><span data-segmentid="228" class="cx-segment">[[美國唱片業協會|美国唱片业协会]](RIAA)为它颁发了白金唱片认证<ref name="abl riaa">{{cite web|url=http://riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?resultpage=1&table=SEARCH_RESULTS&action=&title=A%20beautiful%20lie&artist=30%20seconds%20to%20mars&format=&debutLP=&category=&sex=&releaseDate=&requestNo=&type=&level=&label=&company=&certificationDate=&awardDescription=&catalogNo=&aSex=&rec_id=&charField=&gold=&platinum=&multiPlat=&level2=&certDate=&album=&id=&after=&before=&startMonth=1&endMonth=1&startYear=1958&endYear=2009&sort=Artist&perPage=25|title=Recording Industry Association of America: Gold & Platinum|accessdate=2013-07-03|publisher=[[RIAA|RIAA]]|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924151606/http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?resultpage=1|archivedate=2015-09-24|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，在其他的一些国家和地区，它也达到了当地白金唱片和金唱片的标准。<ref name="10years2"/> 专辑</span><span data-segmentid="230" class="cx-segment">的第一支单曲[[Attack_(Thirty_Seconds_to_Mars_song)|Attack]]于2005年6月6日在电台上首次亮相，并在它发行后的首周内成为了美国[[Modern_rock|现代摇滚乐]]电台播出最多的歌曲。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=30 Seconds to Mars Comes to Montgomery's Off the Wagon|last=Simmons|first=Darryn|date=August 4, 2005|journal=Montgomery Advertiser}}</ref> </span><span data-segmentid="234" class="cx-segment">在2005年期间，</span><span data-segmentid="230" class="cx-segment">30秒上</span><span data-segmentid="234" class="cx-segment">火星</span><span data-segmentid="230" class="cx-segment">与乐队</span><span data-segmentid="234" class="cx-segment">[[Chevelle_(band)|Chevelle]]、[[音魔合唱團|音魔合唱团]]以及[[The_Used|The Used]]完成了巡演。 2006年3月，</span><span data-segmentid="238" class="cx-segment">该乐队开启了他们的首次领衔巡演[[Forever_Night,_Never_Day_Tour|Forever Night, Never Day Tour]]。 与此同时，乐队发布了该张</span><span data-segmentid="240" class="cx-segment">专辑的第二支单曲[[The_Kill|''The Kill (Bury Me)'']]。这首歌在美国[[Alternative_Songs|公告牌现代摇滚歌曲榜]]上最高达到了第3名，并停留了超过50周的时间，在当时创下记录成为历史停留时间最长的歌曲。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.melodic.net/?page=news&id=7430|title=30STM Breaks Modern Rock Record!|accessdate=April 23, 2013|author=Roth|date=February 2, 2007|first=Kaj|work=Melodic|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603220855/http://www.melodic.net/?page=news&id=7430|dead-url=no}}</ref>它的音乐录影带由杰瑞德·雷托假借化名Bartholomew Cubbins导演，受到了经典作品</span>《[[鬼店|闪灵]]》的启发，在发布后<span data-segmentid="240" class="cx-segment">收到了广泛的积极评价和众多的奖项，其中包括[[MTV音樂錄影帶大獎|MTV音乐录影带大奖]]中的MTV2 Award。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/30-seconds-to-mars-video-the-kill-wins-fan-driven-mtv2-award-at-2006-mtv-video-music-awards-55751962.html|title=30 Seconds To Mars Video 'The Kill' Wins Fan-Driven MTV2 Award at 2006 MTV Video Music Awards|accessdate=August 29, 2013|date=September 1, 2006|publisher=[[PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121227092739/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/30-seconds-to-mars-video-the-kill-wins-fan-driven-mtv2-award-at-2006-mtv-video-music-awards-55751962.html|archive-date=2012-12-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref></span>
