支单曲发行。</span> <span data-segmentid="274" class="cx-segment">它的音乐录影</span><span data-segmentid="272" class="cx-segment">带是</span><span data-segmentid="274" class="cx-segment">在格陵兰岛拍摄的，地点位于</span><span data-segmentid="272" class="cx-segment">北极圈</span><span data-segmentid="274" class="cx-segment">以北</span><span data-segmentid="272" class="cx-segment">200</span><span data-segmentid="274" class="cx-segment">英里的冰川上</span><span data-segmentid="272" class="cx-segment">。它的</span><span data-segmentid="274" class="cx-segment">销售</span><span data-segmentid="272" class="cx-segment">收益</span><span data-segmentid="274" class="cx-segment">用以支持[[Natural_Resources_Defense_Council|自然资源保护委员会]]的工作。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rocksound.tv/news/read/30-seconds-to-mars-a-beautiful-lie?|title=30 Seconds To Mars ‘A Beautiful Lie’|accessdate=July 26, 2011|date=January 30, 2008|work=[[Rock_Sound|Rock Sound]]|archive-date=2020-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818152453/https://www.rocksound.tv/news/read/30-seconds-to-mars-a-beautiful-lie|dead-url=no}}</ref></span> <span data-segmentid="276" class="cx-segment">在11</span><span data-segmentid="274" class="cx-segment">月6日的</span><span data-segmentid="276" class="cx-segment">[[2008年MTV歐洲音樂大獎|2008年MTV欧洲音乐大奖]]上，30秒上火星凭借A Beautiful Lie赢得了他们第二个最佳摇滚奖和[[MTV_Europe_Music_Award_for_Best_Video|最佳音乐录音带大奖]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1598808/mtv-europe-music-awards-dominated-by-americans.jhtml|title=Americans Katy Perry, Britney Spears, Kanye West, 30 Seconds To Mars Dominate 2008 MTV EMAs|accessdate=August 28, 2013|author=Kaufman|date=November 7, 2008|first=Gil|publisher=MTV News. Viacom Media Networks|archive-date=2013-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213203433/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1598808/mtv-europe-music-awards-dominated-by-americans.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref></span>

