<span data-segmentid="281" class="cx-segment">2008年8月，30秒上火星开始录制他们的第三张录音室专辑''[[This_Is_War|《全面开战》]]'' 。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.melodic.net/?page=news&id=11063|title=Jared Leto Responds To Virgin Suing 30 Seconds To Mars|accessdate=August 29, 2013|author=Spinelli|date=August 18, 2008|first=Tom|work=Melodic|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923034048/http://www.melodic.net/?page=news&id=11063|archivedate=2013-09-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>这一次，乐队与制作人</span><span data-segmentid="283" class="cx-segment">[[Flood_(producer)|Flood]]及[[Steve_Lillywhite|Steve Lillywhite]]合作。 30秒上</span><span data-segmentid="286" class="cx-segment">火星曾试图</span><span data-segmentid="283" class="cx-segment">在</span><span data-segmentid="286" class="cx-segment">''美丽的谎言'' 巡演后与一个新的厂牌签约，这促使了[[EMI|EMI]]（维京唱片的母公司）向他们提起诉讼，索赔3000万美元。</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">EMI称，</span><span data-segmentid="286" class="cx-segment">乐队</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">未能</span><span data-segmentid="286" class="cx-segment">完成他们在1999年的合约（维京唱片所加入的乐队与Immortal Records之间的合约）中所承诺的</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">五张专辑</span><span data-segmentid="286" class="cx-segment">，还缺少</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">三张</span><span data-segmentid="286" class="cx-segment">。</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment"><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/virgin-emi-sue-30-seconds-to-mars-for-30-million-leto-fights-back-20080818|title=Virgin/EMI Sue 30 Seconds to Mars for $30 Million, Leto Fights Back|accessdate=July 29, 2011|author=Kreps|date=August 18, 2008|first=Daniel|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|archive-date=2013-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130311215547/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/virgin-emi-sue-30-seconds-to-mars-for-30-million-leto-fights-back-20080818|dead-url=no}}</ref></span> <span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">杰瑞德·雷托</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">针对</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">诉讼中</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">提出</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">的一些</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">法律主张</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">作出答复，指出“</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">在</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">加利福尼亚州</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">的</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">法律</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">之下——我们居住在那里并签署了这一合约</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">，一个</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">人</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">不能受到一项</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">合约</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">的捆绑超过七年。</span><span data-segmentid="288" class="cx-segment">”</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">30秒上</span><span data-segmentid="290" class="cx-segment">火星</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">签约后已经过了</span><span data-segmentid="290" class="cx-segment">九年，因此乐队决定行使他们</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">的“</span><span data-segmentid="290" class="cx-segment">法律权利</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">以</span><span data-segmentid="290" class="cx-segment">终止我们的旧的、过</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">时</span><span data-segmentid="290" class="cx-segment">的</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">合同</span><span data-segmentid="290" class="cx-segment">——根据法律规定</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">这一合约</span><span data-segmentid="290" class="cx-segment">是无效的。</span><span data-segmentid="289" class="cx-segment">”</span><span data-segmentid="290" class="cx-segment"><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1592982/20080818/30_seconds_to_mars.jhtml|title=30 Seconds To Mars' Jared Leto Says $30 Million Lawsuit Against Band Is 'Ridiculously Overblown'|accessdate=July 29, 2011|author=Harris|date=August 18, 2008|first=Chris|publisher=MTV News. Viacom Media Networks|archive-date=2010-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101124085254/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1592982/20080818/30_seconds_to_mars.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref></span>

<span data-segmentid="291" class="cx-segment">经过近一年的诉讼对峙，2009年4月28日，乐队宣布这一案件已经得到解决。<ref name="settle">{{Cite news|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2009/04/30-seconds-to-mars-and-emi-make-nice-new-album-due-this-fall.html|title=30 Seconds to Mars and EMI make nice, new album due this fall|date=April 28, 2009|first=Todd|author=Martens|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|accessdate=July 29, 2011|archive-date=2012-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120720021228/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2009/04/30-seconds-to-mars-and-emi-make-nice-new-album-due-this-fall.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> </span><span data-segmentid="292" class="cx-segment">根据几十年前一起涉及女演员[[奥丽维亚·德哈维兰|奥丽维亚·德哈维兰]]的合约诉讼案件中对被告人的辩护成立的情况，30秒上火星这一案件得到了相类似的裁定。 </span><span data-segmentid="294" class="cx-segment">雷托解释说，“加利福尼亚州上诉法院裁定，在加利福尼亚州任何服务合同在七年之后都应失效，在德哈维兰利用这一规定终止了她与[[华纳兄弟|华纳兄弟]]之间的合同后，这便被称为[[De_Havilland_Law|德哈维兰法律]]。”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/nov/29/entertainment/la-ca-30-seconds-to-mars29-2009nov29|title=30 Seconds to Mars soars|accessdate=July 29, 2011|author=Brown|date=November 29, 2009|first=August|work=Los Angeles Times|archive-date=2012-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103172434/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/nov/29/entertainment/la-ca-30-seconds-to-mars29-2009nov29|dead-url=no}}</ref> 随后</span><span data-segmentid="297" class="cx-segment">，30秒上</span><span data-segmentid="294" class="cx-segment">火星</span><span data-segmentid="297" class="cx-segment">与EMI签订了一份新的合同。<ref name="settle" /></span> <span data-segmentid="298" class="cx-segment">雷托称，乐队与EMI之间的分歧已经达成和解，之所以做出这一决定是因为“EMI</span><span data-segmentid="297" class="cx-segment">在</span><span data-segmentid="298" class="cx-segment">处理我们的忧虑和困难</span><span data-segmentid="297" class="cx-segment">时</span><span data-segmentid="298" class="cx-segment">所表现出来的</span><span data-segmentid="297" class="cx-segment">意愿和热情</span><span data-segmentid="298" class="cx-segment">，[以及]能够与那么一个对30秒上火星</span><span data-segmentid="297" class="cx-segment">如此投入和热诚的团队</span><span data-segmentid="298" class="cx-segment">重新合作的机会。”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1610285/20090429/30_seconds_to_mars.jhtml|title=30 Seconds To Mars Talk Settlement With EMI|accessdate=July 29, 2011|author=Montgomery|date=April 29, 2009|first=James|publisher=MTV News. Viacom Media Networks|archive-date=2012-02-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65jmZxGPh?url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1610285/exclusive-30-seconds-mars-talk-settlement-with-emi.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref></span>

<span data-segmentid="299" class="cx-segment">为了能让他们的歌迷参与到''《全面开战》''</span>的制作中，30秒上火星在洛杉矶的Avalon Club举办了一个名为''峰会''（The Summit）的活动。<span data-segmentid="299" class="cx-segment">他们邀请歌迷录制和声和打击乐伴奏。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1610134/30-seconds-mars-talk-fan-summit.jhtml|title=30 Seconds To Mars Talk Fan Summit|accessdate=August 30, 2013|author=Montgomery|date=April 28, 2009|first=James|publisher=MTV News. Viacom Media Networks|archive-date=2013-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929161622/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1610134/30-seconds-mars-talk-fan-summit.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> 经过第一次峰会的成功</span><span data-segmentid="300" class="cx-segment">，乐队在八个不同的国家也举行了这样的活动，并将活动规模扩大到线上。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/267799/30-seconds-to-mars-solicits-fan-input-via-twitter|title=30 Seconds To Mars Solicits Fan Input Via Twitter|accessdate=August 30, 2013|author=Benson|date=August 10, 2009|first=John|work=Billboard|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922095217/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/267799/30-seconds-to-mars-solicits-fan-input-via-twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref> 同时，乐队邀请歌迷提交自己的面部特写照片，用此</span><span data-segmentid="301" class="cx-segment">为专辑制作了2000个不同的独立封面。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://noisecreep.com/30-seconds-to-mars-get-fans-involved-with-album-artwork/|title=30 Seconds to Mars Get Fans Involved With Album Artwork|accessdate=August 30, 2013|author=Lipshutz|date=February 12, 2010|first=Jason S|publisher=[[Noisecreep|Noisecreep]]. [[Townsquare_Media|Townsquare Media]]|archive-date=2020-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818145218/https://noisecreep.com/30-seconds-to-mars-get-fans-involved-with-album-artwork/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 雷托将</span><span data-segmentid="302" class="cx-segment">''全面开战'' 形容为一张关于“生存”的专辑：“这是一场在创作上持续两年的抗争，虽然很凶猛和艰难，但我们得到了非常有创造力的成果。所有的这些不利因素，在事后看来，都使我们更加坚强，使这张专辑更加强大。”<ref name="survival2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/30-seconds-to-mars-sing-about-survival-on-this-is-war-20091208|title=30 Seconds To Mars Sing About Survival on "This Is War"|accessdate=August 29, 2012|author=Harris|date=December 8, 2009|first=Chris|work=Rolling Stone|archive-date=2012-04-02|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66cUSFc5H?url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/30-seconds-to-mars-sing-about-survival-on-this-is-war-20091208|dead-url=no}}</ref></span>

