<span data-segmentid="352" class="cx-segment">2013年2月，[[Up_in_the_Air_(song)|''Up in the Air'']]被宣布将会成为第四张专辑首支单曲。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1702763/thirty-seconds-to-mars-up-in-the-air-outer-space.jhtml|title=Thirty Seconds To Mars To Launch New Single ... Into Outer Space|accessdate=September 10, 2013|author=Montgomery|date=February 28, 2013|first=James|publisher=MTV News. Viacom Media Networks|archive-date=2014-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314023004/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1702763/thirty-seconds-to-mars-up-in-the-air-outer-space.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> 通过与</span><span data-segmentid="354" class="cx-segment">[[美国国家航空航天局|美国国家航空航天局]]的合作，30秒火星让Up in the Air的第一份拷贝登上了[[SpaceX_CRS-2|SpaceX CRS-2]]任务中的[[龙飞船|“龙”号飞船]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/02/28/thirty-seconds-to-mars-up-in-the-air-space-nasa_n_2781121.html|title=Thirty Seconds To Mars, 'Up In The Air' To Be Sent Into Space By NASA|accessdate=September 10, 2013|author=Makarechi|date=February 28, 2013|first=Kia|work=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|archive-date=2015-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151221194025/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/02/28/thirty-seconds-to-mars-up-in-the-air-space-nasa_n_2781121.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 这一计划在2013年3月1日实施，随着</span><span data-segmentid="358" class="cx-segment">[[獵鷹9號運載火箭|猎鹰9号运载火箭]]的升空，有史以来的第一份商业唱片拷贝被送入太空。 </span><span data-segmentid="360" class="cx-segment">2013年3月18日，</span><span data-segmentid="358" class="cx-segment">这支单曲在</span><span data-segmentid="360" class="cx-segment">[[国际空间站|国际空间站]]里首播。在乐队成员和[[Expedition_35|Expedition 35]]任务飞行工程师[[Tom_Marshburn|Thomas Marshburn]]的问答环节后，休斯顿市长[[安妮斯·帕克|安妮斯·帕克]]宣布当天为“30秒上火星日”。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.noise11.com/news/30-seconds-to-mars-song-premieres-in-space-video-20130319|title=30 Seconds To Mars Song Premieres In Space|accessdate=September 10, 2013|author=Cashmere|date=March 19, 2013|first=Paul|publisher=[[Noise11|Noise11]]|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104083439/http://www.noise11.com/news/30-seconds-to-mars-song-premieres-in-space-video-20130319|dead-url=no}}</ref></span> <span data-segmentid="365" class="cx-segment">''Up in the Air''于3月18日迎来了它的电台首播，并在次日开放了线上的购买和下载。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Thirty Seconds to Mars Launching New Single Into Space|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/30-seconds-to-mars-launching-new-single-into-space-20130228|accessdate=October 25, 2014|work=Rolling Stone|date=February 28, 2013|archive-date=2017-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171124064219/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/30-seconds-to-mars-launching-new-single-into-space-20130228|dead-url=no}}</ref> 这首</span><span data-segmentid="366" class="cx-segment">歌曲到在美国[[Alternative_Songs|公告牌另类歌曲榜]]上最高达到了第3位，并在海外市场上取得了成功。<ref name="USalt2">{{Cite news|title=30 Seconds to Mars: Artist Chart History|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/431915/30-seconds-to-mars/chart?f=377|accessdate=May 12, 2015|work=Billboard|archive-date=2019-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616092314/https://www.billboard.com/artist/431915/30-seconds-to-mars/chart?f=377|dead-url=yes}}</ref></span>

<span data-segmentid="368" class="cx-segment">2013年5月21日，通过[[环球音乐集团|环球音乐集团]]，30秒上火星在美国发布了''《爱 欲 信 + 梦》''。 这张</span><span data-segmentid="370" class="cx-segment">专辑获得了大体上积极的评论，并在超过十五个国家的销量榜单中进入前十，其中包括英国和美国。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://hangout.altsounds.com/news/159068-seconds-mars-love-lust-faith-dreams-today.html|title=Thirty Seconds To Mars' Love Lust Faith + Dreams Out Today|accessdate=September 10, 2013|author=Maguire|date=May 21, 2013|first=Chris|publisher=AltSounds|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130719224448/http://hangout.altsounds.com/news/159068-seconds-mars-love-lust-faith-dreams-today.html|archivedate=2013-07-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 6月，</span><span data-segmentid="371" class="cx-segment">乐队开始</span><span data-segmentid="370" class="cx-segment">了</span><span data-segmentid="371" class="cx-segment">他们的</span><span data-segmentid="370" class="cx-segment">巡演</span><span data-segmentid="371" class="cx-segment">[[Love,_Lust,_Faith_and_Dreams_Tour|Love, Lust, Faith and Dreams Tour]]，其中包括在[[Rock_Werchter|Rock Werchter]]、[[Pinkpop_Festival|Pinkpop Festival]]、[[Rock_in_Rio|Rock in Rio]]和[[Rock_am_Ring|Rock am Ring]]等音乐节上的演出。 专辑的第二支单曲</span><span data-segmentid="377" class="cx-segment">[[Do_or_Die_(Thirty_Seconds_to_Mars_song)|''Do or Die'']]在各个[[Modern_rock|现代摇滚]]电台上获得了不错的表现。而第三支单曲[[City_of_Angels_(song)|''City of Angels'']]的发布引发了评论界的热烈好评，并最终在美国另类音乐榜上达到了第8位。<ref name="USalt2"/><ref>{{Cite journal|title=30 Seconds to Mars shine a light on the 'City of Angels'|last=Cooper|first=Ryan|date=November 16, 2013|journal=Kerrang!|issue=1492}}</ref> </span><span data-segmentid="381" class="cx-segment">在8月25日举行的[[2013年MTV音乐录像带大奖|2013年MTV音乐录影带大奖]]盛典上，''Up in the Air''赢得了[[MTV_Video_Music_Award_for_Best_Rock_Video|最佳摇滚录影带]]。</span>

<span data-segmentid="384" class="cx-segment">30秒上火星上在2014年4月25日宣布，经过与维京唱片多年来充满波折的合作后，他们已经与该厂牌解约。雷托告诉杂志''[[告示牌_(雜誌)|公告牌]]''，“我们对于未来感到自由，清晰和兴奋。 </span><span data-segmentid="386" class="cx-segment">这是最美妙的时期。</span><span data-segmentid="384" class="cx-segment">”</span><span data-segmentid="386" class="cx-segment"><ref>{{Cite news|author=Hampp|first=Andrew|title=Jared Leto On Leaving Virgin, Thirty Seconds To Mars Doc 'Artifact'|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6070010/jared-leto-on-leaving-virgin-thirty-seconds-to-mars-doc-artifact|work=Billboard|date=April 25, 2014|accessdate=April 28, 2014|archive-date=2019-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421112448/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6070010/jared-leto-on-leaving-virgin-thirty-seconds-to-mars-doc-artifact|dead-url=no}}</ref></span> <span data-segmentid="387" class="cx-segment">2014年8月，该乐队与美国摇滚乐队[[聯合公園|Linkin Park]]开展了名为[[Carnivores_Tour|Carnivores Tour]]的联合巡演，在北美洲的各大竞技场和体育场进行演出。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Reed|first=Ryan|title=Linkin Park, 30 Seconds to Mars, AFI to Tour Together|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/linkin-park-30-seconds-to-mars-afi-to-tour-together-20140305|accessdate=July 13, 2014|work=Rolling Stone|date=March 5, 2014|archive-date=2017-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170727162948/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/linkin-park-30-seconds-to-mars-afi-to-tour-together-20140305|dead-url=no}}</ref> 30秒上</span><span data-segmentid="390" class="cx-segment">火星</span><span data-segmentid="387" class="cx-segment">随后</span><span data-segmentid="390" class="cx-segment">推出了</span><span data-segmentid="387" class="cx-segment">名为Camp Mars的音乐夏令营活动</span><span data-segmentid="390" class="cx-segment">。</span><span data-segmentid="387" class="cx-segment">这一活动首次于</span><span data-segmentid="390" class="cx-segment">2015年8月在</span><span data-segmentid="391" class="cx-segment">加利福尼亚州马里布</span><span data-segmentid="390" class="cx-segment">举办</span><span data-segmentid="391" class="cx-segment">，</span><span data-segmentid="390" class="cx-segment">其中</span><span data-segmentid="391" class="cx-segment">包括一系列户外项目和一些DJ摆台。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Spanos|first=Brittany|title=Thirty Seconds to Mars Plot 'Camp Mars' Weekend This Summer|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/thirty-seconds-to-mars-plot-camp-mars-weekend-this-summer-20150616|accessdate=November 6, 2015|work=Rolling Stone|date=June 16, 2015|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120083250/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/thirty-seconds-to-mars-plot-camp-mars-weekend-this-summer-20150616|dead-url=no}}</ref></span>

