<span data-segmentid="395" class="cx-segment">2015年11月3日，30秒上火星正在创作其第五张专辑的消息得到确认。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Payne|first=Chris|title=Jared Leto Teases New Thirty Seconds to Mars Music|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/rock/6752912/thirty-seconds-mars-jared-leto-instagram-new-music-2015|work=Billboard|date=November 3, 2015|accessdate=November 3, 2015|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922084344/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/rock/6752912/thirty-seconds-mars-jared-leto-instagram-new-music-2015|dead-url=no}}</ref> </span><span data-segmentid="396" class="cx-segment">2016年8月，</span><span data-segmentid="395" class="cx-segment">该</span><span data-segmentid="396" class="cx-segment">乐队透露他们与[[新視鏡唱片|新视镜唱片]]签约。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Sharp|first=Tyler|title=Thirty Seconds To Mars tease return with new video|url=http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/thirty_seconds_to_mars_tease_return_with_new_videomarsiscoming|accessdate=August 11, 2016|work=[[Alternative_Press_(music_magazine)|Alternative Press]]|date=August 1, 2016|archive-date=2017-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815024810/http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/thirty_seconds_to_mars_tease_return_with_new_videomarsiscoming|dead-url=no}}</ref> 随后，乐队宣布</span><span data-segmentid="398" class="cx-segment">他们在2017年的5月到9月期间与[[缪斯乐队|缪斯乐队]]和[[PVRIS|PVRIS]]一同进行北美巡演。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://loudwire.com/muse-thirty-seconds-to-mars-2017-north-american-tour/|title=Muse + Thirty Seconds to Mars To Embark on 2017 North American Tour|accessdate=February 6, 2017|author=Hartmann|date=February 6, 2017|first=Graham|work=[[Loudwire|Loudwire]]|publisher=[[Townsquare_Media|Townsquare Media]]|archive-date=2020-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818185402/https://loudwire.com/muse-thirty-seconds-to-mars-2017-north-american-tour/|dead-url=no}}</ref> </span><span data-segmentid="401" class="cx-segment">2017年8月</span><span data-segmentid="398" class="cx-segment">，</span><span data-segmentid="401" class="cx-segment">[[Walk_on_Water_(Thirty_Seconds_to_Mars_song)|''Walk on Water'']]被宣布为该乐队第五张专辑的首支单曲。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Maine|first=Samantha|title=Thirty Seconds To Mars have teased their new single|url=http://www.nme.com/news/music/thirty-seconds-to-mars-new-single-2124570|work=NME|accessdate=August 14, 2017|date=August 14, 2017|archive-date=2020-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818064957/https://www.nme.com/news/music/thirty-seconds-to-mars-new-single-2124570|dead-url=no}}</ref> 之后，30秒上</span><span data-segmentid="403" class="cx-segment">火星</span><span data-segmentid="401" class="cx-segment">在</span><span data-segmentid="403" class="cx-segment">[[2017年MTV音乐录影带大奖|2017年MTV音乐录影带大奖]]盛典上与特邀嘉宾[[Travis_Scott|Travis Scott]]</span><span data-segmentid="406" class="cx-segment">表演了这首歌曲。在这次盛典上，杰瑞德·雷托向那年早些时候去世的[[查斯特·班寧頓|查斯特·班宁顿]]和[[克里斯·康奈爾|克里斯·康奈尔]]致敬，并在社交媒体上受到了关注。</span>

<span data-segmentid="409" class="cx-segment">2018年1月25日，30秒上火星发布[[Dangerous_Night|''Dangerous Night'']]为他们即将到来的第五张专辑中的第二支单曲。<ref>{{Cite news|title=There's a new Thirty Seconds to Mars song|url=http://www.kerrang.com/the-news/theres-a-new-thirty-seconds-to-mars-song/|accessdate=June 14, 2018|work=[[Kerrang!|Kerrang!]]|date=January 25, 2018|archive-date=2020-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818150454/https://www.kerrang.com/the-news/theres-a-new-thirty-seconds-to-mars-song/|dead-url=no}}</ref> </span><span data-segmentid="411" class="cx-segment">2018年2月，乐队正式宣布</span><span data-segmentid="409" class="cx-segment">新的巡演</span><span data-segmentid="411" class="cx-segment">[[Monolith_Tour|Monolith Tour]]，开场表演艺人包括[[月球漫步乐队|月球漫步乐队]]、[[Misterwives|MisterWives]]、[[K._Flay|K.Flay]]、[[Joywave|Joywave]]及[[Welshly_Arms|Welshly Arms]]的。 不久以后，30秒上</span><span data-segmentid="418" class="cx-segment">火星确认''[[America_(Thirty_Seconds_to_Mars_album)|《美利坚》]]''</span>将会是第五张专辑的标题<span data-segmentid="418" class="cx-segment">，它于2018年4月6日发行。这张</span><span data-segmentid="420" class="cx-segment">专辑在评论界收到</span><span data-segmentid="418" class="cx-segment">了两极分化</span><span data-segmentid="420" class="cx-segment">的</span><span data-segmentid="418" class="cx-segment">评价。</span><span data-segmentid="420" class="cx-segment">它首次出现在''[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌两百强专辑榜]]''</span>便排在了第2的位置<span data-segmentid="420" class="cx-segment">，获得了该乐队在这一榜单上的最高名次。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8337801/cardi-b-invasion-of-privacy-debuts-at-no-1-on-billboard-200-album-chart|title=Cardi B's 'Invasion of Privacy' Debuts at No. 1 on Billboard 200 Chart|accessdate=June 14, 2018|author=Caulfield|date=April 15, 2018|first=Keith|work=Billboard|archive-date=2019-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190703074852/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8337801/cardi-b-invasion-of-privacy-debuts-at-no-1-on-billboard-200-album-chart|dead-url=no}}</ref> ''《美利坚》''</span>在其他十<span data-segmentid="422" class="cx-segment">七个国家也进入到了销量前十，其中在德国和奥地利取得了第一。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.austriancharts.at/showitem.asp?interpret=Thirty+Seconds+to+Mars&titel=America&cat=a|title=Thirty Seconds to Mars – America|accessdate=June 14, 2018|publisher=Hung Medien|archive-date=2020-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818152807/https://austriancharts.at/showitem.asp?interpret=Thirty+Seconds+to+Mars&titel=America&cat=a|dead-url=no}}</ref></span>

